Sabrina Bartlett https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sabrina_Bartlett 0 Sabrina Bartlett is an English actress. She is known for playing the part of Sophia in Da Vinci's Demons. In 2016, Bartlett appeared in the sixth-season finale of the HBO series Game of Thrones as a disguise of Arya Stark. She also appeared as Princess Isabella in the first season of the History series Knightfall. Sabrina_Bartlett is an_English_actress .
